be30b9","tid":900510,"uid":66242,"like":13,"dislike":34,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"對上一個可能係鄧麗君"},{"pid":"aa1d19140e1301d710569cf477da5a71b7592d10","tid":900510,"uid":75232,"like":14,"dislike":98,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"個靈堂用殘體字嘅？"},{"pid":"38636fcb57dfdc59b980f6215cdf8cd67fe91539","tid":900510,"uid":163350,"like":104,"dislike":9,"score":95,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cde90a2712c67ba3cbd4516895a78cd6d6dd5ae","tid":900510,"uid":16061,"like":35,"dislike":7,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"我整個特朗普敬輓都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd1ca586c5d43815f10bcda468a3f166fc78bc5","tid":900510,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"【文匯網訊】11月2日，中共中央總書記、國家主席習近平對查良鏞(金庸)先生的逝世表示哀悼，對其親屬表示慰問。<br />\n<br />\n10月30日下午，香港著名作家、中國文聯榮譽委員、中國作協名譽副主席查良鏞先生在香港逝世，享年94歲。<br />\n<br />\n查良鏞先生逝世後，李克強、韓正、孫春蘭、黃坤明、朱鎔基、溫家寶、張德江、李嵐清、劉延東、李源潮、王漢斌、廖暉等同志也以不同方式表示哀悼，並向其親屬表示慰問。<br />\n<br />\n11月2日晚，中央政府駐港聯絡辦主任王志民專程到查良鏞先生家中，向查先生夫人林樂怡女士轉達了習近平總書記等中央領導同志對查良鏞先生逝世的哀悼和對親屬的慰問。林樂怡女士對習總書記等中央領導的關心問候表示感謝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.wenweipo.com/2018/11/02/IN1811020053.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F11%2F02%2FIN1811020053.htm&d=YnhgAe5tbPrEvEKdRa5Cshv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=04b3c9e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com/2018/11/02/IN1811020053.htm</a>"},{"pid":"575e05ac50aefa0d2898b06a2753105f9eaf88af","tid":900510,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"唔知stan lee死侵侵有無講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc0043839bdedf5e0d9d7c5b6bb4bd7f402e6da","tid":900510,"uid":35221,"like":150,"dislike":2,"score":148,"quote":{"pid":"aa1d19140e1301d710569cf477da5a71b7592d10","tid":900510,"uid":75232,"like":14,"dislike":98,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"個靈堂用殘體字嘅？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"明代郭一經《字學三正．體製上．時俗杜撰字》曰：「衆：俗作众。」<br />\n<br />\n季旭昇：「眾」字下从三人，「眾」簡省上部、存其下部，筆畫稍變則作「众」耳，據此，「众」為「眾」之異體，可從。<br />\n<br />\n「众」至少明代已有，亦「眾」字之異體。只係後來鄰國共匪納入殘體字方案入面，其實古已有之。"},{"pid":"81a03dfb50925005b355097e4141d7c78d2a3be4","tid":900510,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:06:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔用簡體字"},{"pid":"50273f08f00e9d166eb55ff98fea217e2cc8da77","tid":900510,"uid":75232,"like":40,"dislike":8,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"dfc0043839bdedf5e0d9d7c5b6bb4bd7f402e6da","tid":900510,"uid":35221,"like":150,"dislike":2,"score":148,"quote":{"pid":"aa1d19140e1301d710569cf477da5a71b7592d10","tid":900510,"uid":75232,"like":14,"dislike":98,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"個靈堂用殘體字嘅？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"明代郭一經《字學三正．體製上．時俗杜撰字》曰：「衆：俗作众。」<br />\n<br />\n季旭昇：「眾」字下从三人，「眾」簡省上部、存其下部，筆畫稍變則作「众」耳，據此，「众」為「眾」之異體，可從。<br />\n<br />\n「众」至少明代已有，亦「眾」字之異體。只係後來鄰國共匪納入殘體字方案入面，其實古已有之。"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:06:36.000Z","msg":"我係指個覽字嘅左上角..."},{"pid":"7067ac6785d5b6c06b67ed37f080b77825a442be","tid":900510,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:08:04.000Z","msg":"拋妻棄子"},{"pid":"057bd27cb187bacc70bfbeaf3b0b4bb4e7ecc4a1","tid":900510,"uid":12347,"like":23,"dislike":9,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"50273f08f00e9d166eb55ff98fea217e2cc8da77","tid":900510,"uid":75232,"like":40,"dislike":8,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"dfc0043839bdedf5e0d9d7c5b6bb4bd7f402e6da","tid":900510,"uid":35221,"like":150,"dislike":2,"score":148,"quote":{"pid":"aa1d19140e1301d710569cf477da5a71b7592d10","tid":900510,"uid":75232,"like":14,"dislike":98,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"個靈堂用殘體字嘅？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"明代郭一經《字